<HEADLINE> Egypt Ready for Cairo International Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, February 1 (Xinhua) -- The Egyptian exhibition authority
has finished preparations for the 29th Cairo International Fair to
be held from March 16 to 29, authority Chairman Rushdi Sakr said
here today.
</P>
<P>
As many as 235 foreign companies from 34 countries have
announced that they will participate in the upcoming annual fair
so far, Rushdi Sakr said.
</P>
<P>
He said a total of 45 countries are expected to exhibit their
products in the exhibition.
</P>
<P>
Rushdi Sakr said his exhibition authority has sent out
invitations to ministers of economy and trade of the participant
countries to visit Egypt on the sidelines of the exhibition with a
view to promote economic cooperation between Egypt and those
countries. 
</P>
