<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, February 1 (Xinhua) -- China beat the Philippines
7-0 and Hong Kong downed Macao 4-1 in the second-round matches at
the 11th Asian Cup Group Two soccer qualifying tournament here
this evening.
