<HEADLINE> Forums Held to Promote Reunification </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, February 1 (Xinhua) -- The China Council for the
Promotion of Peaceful Reunification (CCPPR) and the Liaison
Subcommittee for Taiwan, Hong Kong and Macao Compatriots and
Overseas Chinese of the Chinese People's Political Consultative
Conference (CPPCC) held a forum here today to mark the first
anniversary of President Jiang Zemin's speech entitled "Continue
to Promote the Reunification of the Motherland".
</P>
<P>
