ceasefire, the situation in the early stages is still volatile and
fraught with problems."
</P>
<P>
Syed Hamid said the Malaysian government would spend more than
100 million Malaysian ringgit (about 40 million US dollars) in
sending troops there, excluding the cost of equipment.  
