Champions Cup in December while the Fourth women's championship
would be held in China in May.
</P>
<P>
Kuwait was the winner of the Eighth Asian Cup which was held in
Kuwait in 1995 and participated in the 14th Handball World Cup in
Iceland of the year.
</P>
<P>
It will also represent Asia in the Summer Olympic Games in
Atlanta, Untied States this summer. 
