the Dhaka Medical College Hospital, the authorities concerned
confirmed.
</P>
<P>
It was learnt that different political parties, teachers and
student organizations strongly condemned the police action. The
mainstream opposition parties have called for an 8-hour strike on
February 3 to protest "the killing, repression and arrest of
university students." 
