<HEADLINE> Mexico-CA Summit to Focus on Political Issues </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SAN JOSE, January 31 (Xinhua) -- Costa Rican Foreign Minister
Fernando Naranjo emphasized today that political issues will be
the focus of a summit to be held by Mexico and Central American
countries on February 15.
</P>
