The Nasdaq composite index rose 6.51 to 1,057.81.
</P>
<P>
At the American Stock Exchange, the market value index rose
3.14 to 554.10.
</P>
<P>
The stock market had broken through record highs on Friday,
Monday and Tuesday, as investors anticipated a rate cut aimed at
boosting economy.
</P>
<P>
The central bank cut the Federal Funds rate and the discount
rate by 0.25 percentage points.  
</P>
